Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:39.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}As we journeyed in search\nof Naraku's whereabouts,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.77,0:01:41.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}three young monkey sprites\nappeared before us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.30,0:01:44.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Clumsy, scatterbrained\nand quick to jump to conclusions...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:45.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}yet too cute to hate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.91,0:01:47.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}The three monkey sprites were\nin search of{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:50.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}the sacred object which housed\ntheirMonkey God.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.78,0:01:55.58,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}We finally found it in a pickling tub\nbeing used as a weight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.82,0:01:57.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the Monkey God said\nsomething very strange.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.48,0:02:01.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}A huge evil aura had flown overhead\nin the direction of the ox-tiger,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.69,0:02:03.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}then suddenly disappeared.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:06.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No doubt about it!\NIt's Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.26,0:02:08.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Ox and tiger?\NThat's northeast?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.30,0:02:10.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.46,0:02:11.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.50,0:02:14.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We know which way to go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We head northeast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:28.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! She's supposed to come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:33.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:36.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:38.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.13,0:02:42.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome didn't catch a cold\nbecause she wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.36,0:02:44.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:48.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's for the best. This trip is going\nto be a long one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:53.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'll use this time\nto get things ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! I have to prep\nall my gadgets.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:00.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So your cold is actually\na blessing, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's right.\NSo don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Damn! Hurry and get well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.75,0:03:09.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, I understand\nyourhaste.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:11.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But don't blame Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.36,0:03:12.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:13.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.29,0:03:15.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:20.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Geez! I'm not blaming you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:24.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.50,0:03:27.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome will recover quicker\nif Inuyasha isn't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.91,0:03:31.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's a problem that\NOld Kaede is away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:35.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You have a terrible fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:38.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, why don't you\ngo home to the modern age?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:40.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.89,0:03:43.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There are good doctors there, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And you seem to have\ngood medicine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.79,0:03:46.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:50.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but I'm going\nhome for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.30,0:03:53.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.70,0:03:56.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now come, Kagome...\non my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:58.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can you manage, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:03:59.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:04.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.61,0:04:08.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, she'll be staying\nhome again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.98,0:04:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh no, it's just a cold.\NIt's for real this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi is absent again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This time, she has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.43,0:04:23.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- A cold?\N- Only a cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.84,0:04:30.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well? How's your appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:31.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't have any.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then I'll make you something\nwarm to drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:35.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You can take yourmedicine\nafterthat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:43.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's been awhile since we saw her,\nyet she has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:45.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was cold\nback there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She should take her time\nand recover completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.36,0:04:51.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.09,0:04:54.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,For a mere cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:58.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Until now, she stayed home\nfor all kinds of strange ailments.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.20,0:04:59.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.10,0:05:01.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shall we go visit her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:02.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Visit her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.37,0:05:06.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She won't be hospitalized for a cold.\NKagome will be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.17,0:05:08.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I get it!\NGood idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:11.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll be nice to\nvisit Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you going to Higurashi's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.28,0:05:14.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Hojo...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:17.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome has a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see... a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.99,0:05:22.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Would you like to go visit her, too?\N- I see... Cold, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.39,0:05:25.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if he's going\nto see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:26.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Adelicate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:32.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:34.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do not panic, Rikichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay calm and attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, but we haven't done\nthis in so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:40.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.11,0:05:45.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha and the others aren't here.\NWe must deal with it ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.45,0:05:48.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:52.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now! Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:57.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Kaede!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:05.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Get out of my way, punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.57,0:06:12.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:16.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.51,0:06:19.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Many demons have been\nacting up lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:23.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Some even terrorize\nareas where humans live.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:26.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It seems Naraku's disappearance\ncaused all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:28.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons lay low while\nhe's around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:30.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now they're doing as they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.93,0:06:37.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Want some more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.48,0:06:50.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:53.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.11,0:06:56.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did he come to save us?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.55,0:07:00.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... he's not that\ncommendable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're in the way.\NMove!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:12.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Punk! Just who do\nyou think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who cares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.77,0:07:16.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I have business in this swamp.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This swamp is my territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:23.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Keep it up and\NI'll swallow you head first!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Head, huh?\NThis head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Take... that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:38.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.64,0:07:52.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.61,0:07:56.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This valley belongs to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This waterfall...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.46,0:08:13.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:16.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.76,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not listening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Lady Kaede...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The demons aren't\nappearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.84,0:08:28.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder if they\nescaped somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:36.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:38.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... since we're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.42,0:08:40.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You came to visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:41.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.46,0:08:43.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's yourtemperature?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:44.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A slight fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.69,0:08:46.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's yourthroat?\NAre you all stuffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.49,0:08:47.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've been coughing still.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.09,0:08:49.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here, for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.73,0:08:50.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Even if it's just a cold,\ntake care.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.50,0:08:57.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's right. You've been so\nsickly lately, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.10,0:08:58.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.30,0:09:00.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Does he come to\nvisit you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:01.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know... the delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:05.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He wouldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:06.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:08.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not kind then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:14.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with all this?\NHurry and get well!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.69,0:09:17.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.39,0:09:19.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... far, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:20.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.79,0:09:23.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone named Hojo is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:25.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.07,0:09:27.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.30,0:09:30.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo... What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:32.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard you caught a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:33.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I came to pay\nyou a visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I gave it a lot of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.14,0:09:40.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wondered just what I could\ndo for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is the only thing I could\nthink of that's good foryour health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.75,0:09:48.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:49.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.59,0:09:50.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.49,0:09:53.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are charms for\ngood health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.03,0:09:57.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But ljust remembered that\nyourfamily owns a shrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Our charms don't work\ntoo well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.53,0:10:02.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,These are dumbbells.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.10,0:10:07.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think you should\nbuild up your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:09.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:10.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You still have something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.68,0:10:14.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why don't you ask him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:25.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:26.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What happened to Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:28.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We sent herback home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.59,0:10:29.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:33.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We thought she'd get better\ncare in her own home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So we sent herback.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.97,0:10:37.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,S-She went home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.37,0:10:39.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just when I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:40.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where did you go\nwithout me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.34,0:10:45.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo! Why you...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:47.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:50.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:58.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, looks delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Gifts forus?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.36,0:11:03.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Er... no... he's probably preparing\nforthe long journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.46,0:11:06.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:12.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm sure I put it away in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.44,0:11:14.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Grandpa.\NWhat're you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.64,0:11:16.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh! Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.98,0:11:19.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The secret medicine passed down\nthrough generations of Higurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.88,0:11:21.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It works on any and all illnesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I finally found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:25.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.55,0:11:28.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome's cold will be cured\nin a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.49,0:11:30.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Oh well...\N- Just wait, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Oh, Buyo!\N- I'll have in ten minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.73,0:11:39.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Grandpa... sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.23,0:11:41.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... what have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.37,0:11:49.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.28,0:11:51.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.81,0:11:53.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.61,0:11:55.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's been asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.28,0:11:57.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But now she has some visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.72,0:11:59.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.12,0:12:02.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All the boys went wild.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:04.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:06.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stop already.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It became the talk of\nmy class, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:10.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Really?! Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.90,0:12:14.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll bet it's all over\nthe school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.60,0:12:15.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.97,0:12:18.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.81,0:12:26.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.01,0:12:28.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.25,0:12:29.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,To Kagome's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:31.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, ljust came to see\nhow she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.98,0:12:33.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're so kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.49,0:12:35.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:37.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}He doesn't know, afterall.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.19,0:12:40.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That Kagome has a boyfriend.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:44.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Kagome's boyfriend\nis also kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.56,0:12:45.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:49.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um... were you just\ntalking about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:52.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No! Kagome has...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.81,0:12:54.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:57.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's someone who's\nbeen bothering Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.14,0:12:58.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.08,0:12:59.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone who won't even\ncome to see her when she's sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.08,0:13:03.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}School seems so much fun.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:07.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:09.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sota, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.62,0:13:11.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:15.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:16.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.00,0:13:17.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing. Just came to see\nhow you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.00,0:13:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You came to visit me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.94,0:13:26.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shippo and Sango were worried!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:29.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But I'm the only one\nable to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:30.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.98,0:13:34.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I feel better, but my fever\nwon't go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.31,0:13:36.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm feeling a little tired, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:44.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l-I didn't come here to\ntake you back, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.59,0:13:46.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'd bettertake care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Better if you rest here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:50.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.40,0:13:57.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.74,0:13:58.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:03.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.51,0:14:07.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is there something troubling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.98,0:14:10.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Troubling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.82,0:14:12.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.56,0:14:18.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish you would confide\nin me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.73,0:14:25.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll do whatever I can for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.57,0:14:28.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.57,0:14:32.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Since we're going out, it's the least...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.11,0:14:34.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Umm... huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:38.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't you think this will be on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:47.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.32,0:14:49.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the comprehension test.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.46,0:14:50.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Test?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:54.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And it's going to be used to\ndetermine our course of study.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:55.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forhigh school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.96,0:14:58.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Have you been studying\nduring your absence?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.47,0:15:03.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.60,0:15:06.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Besides, she's noteven sure if\nshe can make it to school tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.17,0:15:10.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What'll we be tested on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:11.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:13.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You plan on taking the test\nwhen you're sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:13.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Higurashi, are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:30.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I knew it! There {\i1}is{\i0} something\ntroubling you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.63,0:15:32.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Please help me study!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:36.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it okay for herto\nstay up?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:41.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's an emphasis on\nmath and science.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So you should memorize\nyourformulas and equations...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.84,0:15:47.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:49.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.62,0:15:53.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No. Please continue, Hojo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you, Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:00.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.76,0:16:02.42,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll be seeing you, Higurashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.69,0:16:05.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.83,0:16:06.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:08.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.73,0:16:10.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See you. Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:11.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.41,0:16:14.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:19.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.01,0:16:20.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.18,0:16:23.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This test thing...\NIs it that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:24.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.02,0:16:29.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the sense in taking a test\nif you don'tget overyour cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:31.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But once I'm better,\NI'll have to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:32.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So I have to study.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:34.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Getting better is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Both are important.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just stay in bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.03,0:16:40.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.80,0:16:41.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.80,0:16:43.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I WANTto go to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Go away! Don'tget in the way\nof my studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.97,0:16:49.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.24,0:16:52.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Awright! I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:59.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm such a fool...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:03.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, how do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.22,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll make some rice gruel,\nso eat, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:07.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.33,0:17:12.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They all look so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:15.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We can sell it and\nmake good money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:18.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't think we should\ntouch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:20.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kirara!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.61,0:17:24.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I haven't done a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.14,0:17:26.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't touch a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.38,0:17:27.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.18,0:17:32.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:45.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh... my head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.63,0:17:49.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:52.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Inuyasha!\NYou didn't go back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:54.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I need a cooking fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.54,0:17:55.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Cooking fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.51,0:17:56.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will a gas range do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.45,0:18:05.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.05,0:18:08.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fornourishment,\nthere's nothing like liver!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.02,0:18:12.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boarliver, carp liver,\nchicken liver...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:14.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And medicinal roots\nand herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.73,0:18:16.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, you're gonna\neat all that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.16,0:18:18.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.43,0:18:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,T-Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.73,0:18:20.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.41,0:18:30.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:34.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Here. Medicine. Drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.75,0:18:35.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:38.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It smells!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:41.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If you drink it,\nyou'll get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It'll cure any cold\nin an instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:53.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.67,0:18:55.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bearit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.73,0:18:58.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It may taste bad,\nbut it'll work without fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.54,0:19:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.37,0:19:01.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.27,0:19:04.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If it'll work,\NI'll put up with the taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You sure it'll work?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.18,0:19:10.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Trust me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's drinking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.89,0:19:22.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis is drinking liverpotion!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.60,0:19:27.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Liverpotion...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're right.\NI think it's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:34.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.47,0:19:37.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Nothing doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.28,0:19:41.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But how did you know about\nmaking such medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.11,0:19:44.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... my motherused to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.45,0:19:45.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.55,0:19:47.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She made it foryou?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.25,0:19:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, the ingredients\nare a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:52.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She used dried ingredients.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:54.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I used fresh ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:57.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fresh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.16,0:19:59.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fresh what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.33,0:20:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Fresh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:04.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Anyway, it'll work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:06.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:08.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I said it's nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.54,0:20:10.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry aboutearlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.81,0:20:13.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Forget it! Justgo to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:21.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is that some kind of\nmagic spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.75,0:20:23.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:26.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My motherused to\ndo it long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.76,0:20:27.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.52,0:20:52.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:56.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.49,0:20:58.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:59.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.56,0:21:02.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Much, much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.56,0:21:04.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yourmedicine worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:06.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.23,0:21:10.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I can go to school.\NI'll even pass the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.11,0:21:18.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's no good!\NI'll be late even if I leave now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:20.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I won't make it in time\nforthe test!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.28,0:21:23.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You'll make it if you hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.98,0:21:25.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Buteven if I hurry...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.45,0:21:27.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hurry and change!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:33.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Wait, Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.26,0:21:34.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.33,0:21:36.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Will you make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:37.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,'Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.37,0:21:46.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.64,0:21:47.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's your cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.87,0:21:51.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I slept through the night,\nand I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:52.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What about the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.38,0:21:54.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go forit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.71,0:21:55.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Atta girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.21,0:21:57.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:53.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, Inuyasha... I have to talk to you\nman-to-man.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.33,0:23:54.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.27,0:23:55.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is love?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.67,0:23:56.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is love eternal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.94,0:23:58.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.74,0:24:01.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I... I love Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:03.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, you do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.48,0:24:04.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.54,0:24:07.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll do anything for\nmy darling little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.15,0:24:12.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Sota's Brave Confession of Love"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.72,0:24:14.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is way harderthan\nslaying demons!
